Welcome to Manifest OS — Declare it. Share it. Deploy it.

The installer starts automatically on the main screen. If you are at this
shell, you can relaunch it at any time:

    manifest-gui      graphical installer
    manifest tui      text installer (low-memory / no GPU)

Networking: wired and Wi-Fi connections using DHCP come up automatically.
For Wi-Fi, authenticate with the iwctl utility; for mobile broadband (WWAN)
modems, use mmcli.

Documentation: https://manifest.os
